Class ComponentsFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.appliance.vcenter.settings.v1.config.components.ComponentsFactory

  • public class ComponentsFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    ComponentsFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.appliance.vcenter.settings.v1.config.components package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
